Palm Palm Beach County Sheriffs Office is seeking the whereabouts of Carly A. Sananes, W/F, DOB: 11/12/94, who is approximately 5’5 and 140lbs.  She has brown hair and hazel eyes. 
 
Carly Sananes was last seen on June 2, 2017 at approximately 8:0 pm in the City of Lake Worth. Carly also may be going by the nickname of “Ana.” Anyone with information is asked to contact the Palm Beach County Sheriff’s Office at 561-688-3400.
